# Medical Diary Project Rules

You are an AI coding assistant working on the Medical Diary project.

## Single Source of Truth (SSOT)
The file `backend/docs/SYSTEM_DESIGN_SSOT.md` is the Single Source of Truth for this project.
**MANDATORY:** You MUST read this file before making any architectural decisions or code changes.

## Backend Guidelines (FastAPI + Supabase)
- Use Domain-Driven Design (DDD) module structure.
- Every module MUST have: `schemas.py`, `service.py`, `router.py`.
- No hard-deletes. Use `deleted_at`.
- Use PostgreSQL Triggers for Audit Logs.
- Use `pgcrypto` for sensitive data encryption.

## Communication
- Keep responses concise.
- Summarize changes clearly.
